01:36.288 --> 01:41.024
= Love's Ambition=

01:41.040 --> 01:43.952
=Episode 29=

01:46.554 --> 01:47.994
Mr. Shen, your guest is here.

01:50.554 --> 01:51.194
Haoming.

01:51.754 --> 01:52.474
Mr. Qu.

01:55.034 --> 01:55.953
Long time no see.

01:56.474 --> 01:57.953
Come, give me a hug.

01:58.754 --> 01:59.674
You're still the same.

02:00.034 --> 02:01.114
Not really.

02:01.313 --> 02:03.353
But you are more handsome.

02:04.073 --> 02:05.394
Why didn't you tell me earlier

02:05.394 --> 02:06.274
that you came to me?

02:06.274 --> 02:07.554
Chen Lin could've picked you up.

02:08.354 --> 02:10.074
The driver can also bring me here.

02:11.354 --> 02:12.473
Alright, please have a seat.

02:14.234 --> 02:15.633
Your office is quite spacious

02:15.954 --> 02:16.674
and splendid.

02:17.514 --> 02:19.234
Jinda is indeed splendid.

02:19.873 --> 02:20.713
Have you

02:20.753 --> 02:21.354
met my dad?

02:21.473 --> 02:23.193
I visited your dad long ago.

02:23.873 --> 02:25.153
He invited me

02:25.433 --> 02:26.234
to a meeting,

02:26.313 --> 02:27.313
but I wasn't interested,

02:27.674 --> 02:29.153
so I came to you right away.

02:30.753 --> 02:31.633
Glad to see you.

02:36.153 --> 02:37.713
Dahongpao Tea from Mount Wuyi.

02:37.913 --> 02:39.633
Haoming,

02:40.153 --> 02:41.074
it's been years,

02:41.074 --> 02:42.633
yet you still remember my preference.

02:44.033 --> 02:44.873
I remember

02:45.033 --> 02:47.234
when my dad took me
to Guangdong as a child,

02:47.674 --> 02:49.554
you were the one who took me

02:49.753 --> 02:50.713
to tea houses

02:51.274 --> 02:52.354
to drink Dahongpao Tea.

02:58.114 --> 02:58.633
How is it?

02:58.834 --> 02:59.313
Excellent!

03:01.114 --> 03:01.794
Haoming,

03:03.674 --> 03:04.674
I have

03:04.794 --> 03:05.713
devoted most of my life

03:06.193 --> 03:07.274
to Jinda.

03:08.794 --> 03:09.873
To be honest,

03:11.394 --> 03:13.394
I haven't managed my family well.

03:13.954 --> 03:15.753
And I'm still a bachelor.

03:16.234 --> 03:17.234
I've

03:17.753 --> 03:19.074
watched you grow up.

03:20.433 --> 03:21.753
In my eyes,

03:22.753 --> 03:24.114
you're like my own son.

03:24.753 --> 03:25.313
Mr. Qu.

03:25.674 --> 03:27.193
You are my dad's best friend.

03:28.234 --> 03:29.713
Your dedication to Jinda

03:30.033 --> 03:31.193
has been witnessed by all.

03:31.593 --> 03:32.674
Without your efforts

03:32.794 --> 03:34.354
in the Greater Bay Area,

03:34.713 --> 03:36.313
we wouldn't have achieved that much.

03:36.794 --> 03:37.794
As a junior,

03:38.153 --> 03:39.234
I must learn from you.

03:39.954 --> 03:40.994
I just did what's right.

03:42.674 --> 03:43.234
Haoming.

03:43.834 --> 03:44.794
This time, I came

03:45.433 --> 03:46.633
for one purpose only.

03:47.794 --> 03:49.153
I heard you joined the board,

03:49.394 --> 03:51.313
so I came specially to vote for you.

03:52.033 --> 03:52.954
All these years,

03:53.554 --> 03:54.913
I've always supported your dad.

03:56.074 --> 03:57.074
Now, of course,

03:57.313 --> 03:58.633
I offer you my support.

03:59.873 --> 04:00.954
Don't feel burdened.

04:01.473 --> 04:02.433
Just do what you want.

04:03.633 --> 04:04.354
Thank you, Mr. Qu.

04:07.674 --> 04:08.433
Here. Haoming.

04:09.593 --> 04:10.274
Let's toast.

04:14.354 --> 04:15.913
How's it going?

04:17.594 --> 04:18.714
We've been acquiring

04:18.714 --> 04:20.193
stocks from Jinda's retail investors.

04:21.193 --> 04:22.354
But we still don't

04:22.354 --> 04:23.193
have enough stocks.

04:24.114 --> 04:25.234
Several major shareholders

04:25.234 --> 04:27.474
are reluctant to sell.
I'll figure it out.

04:29.313 --> 04:31.034
If you can uncover that child's

04:31.034 --> 04:32.953
connection to Shen Haoming,

04:33.594 --> 04:34.433
then things

04:34.554 --> 04:35.633
will be much easier.

04:35.914 --> 04:37.193
Weiping and I are working on it.

04:38.234 --> 04:39.393
I need results.

04:40.554 --> 04:41.313
Understood, Mr. Qu.

04:42.154 --> 04:43.234
My people have found out

04:43.914 --> 04:44.794
that Shen Haoming

04:45.154 --> 04:46.674
and Fang Yu did have a child

04:46.674 --> 04:47.714
while studying abroad.

04:48.474 --> 04:50.513
During Fang Yu's pregnancy,
Haoming stayed with her.

04:52.633 --> 04:54.474
But after returning from abroad,

04:54.474 --> 04:55.114
Shen Haoming

04:55.114 --> 04:56.273
remained single.

04:56.873 --> 04:57.873
Where was the child?

04:58.034 --> 05:00.234
Not long after Shen Haoming's returning,

05:00.234 --> 05:01.513
Shen Jinsong and Yu Lan

05:01.914 --> 05:03.794
publicly announced they had given birth

05:03.794 --> 05:04.914
to a second child overseas.

05:07.073 --> 05:07.914
Guess who

05:08.354 --> 05:10.313
the biological father
of this child actually is.

05:10.554 --> 05:12.034
Maybe Shen Haochen isn't

05:13.513 --> 05:14.234
Shen Haoming's

05:14.234 --> 05:15.234
younger brother,

05:16.633 --> 05:17.393
but his son, right?

05:18.073 --> 05:20.114
If this gets exposed...

05:31.594 --> 05:32.154
Chen Lin,

05:34.354 --> 05:35.393
I never thought Mr. Shen's

05:35.393 --> 05:36.393
entry into the board

05:36.393 --> 05:37.513
would go so smoothly.

05:38.114 --> 05:38.953
Of course.

05:39.154 --> 05:40.273
Mr. Shen

05:40.474 --> 05:41.513
truly deserves it.

05:42.114 --> 05:42.674
Thanks.

05:44.234 --> 05:44.794
Now,

05:45.234 --> 05:46.154
all these board members

05:46.193 --> 05:47.154
invite him to dinners.

05:47.433 --> 05:48.594
We have to accompany him

05:48.833 --> 05:49.714
in tonight's dinner.

05:53.474 --> 05:54.714
Why did you sigh?

05:56.994 --> 05:58.433
I need to drive Mr. Shen home.

06:00.114 --> 06:01.474
Today is my girlfriend's birthday.

06:01.994 --> 06:03.114
She has warned me

06:03.554 --> 06:06.313
that if I don't show up,
I'll be off her list.

06:08.994 --> 06:11.753
You have to choose
between career and love.

06:12.994 --> 06:14.393
I am so worried.

06:15.753 --> 06:16.273
Don't worry.

06:16.914 --> 06:17.994
As you are in dilemma,

06:18.953 --> 06:19.914
after tonight's dinner,

06:20.273 --> 06:21.433
I'll drive Mr. Shen home.

06:22.594 --> 06:23.914
But your hand is injured.

06:24.994 --> 06:26.234
Minor injury. No problem.

06:26.873 --> 06:27.794
Leave it to me.

06:27.833 --> 06:28.354
Don't worry.

06:28.794 --> 06:29.354
Seriously?

06:30.034 --> 06:31.154
I'll arrange a driver

06:31.313 --> 06:31.994
to send you both.

06:32.193 --> 06:32.714
I'll go

06:32.714 --> 06:33.633
to request leave now.

06:35.313 --> 06:35.873
Thanks.

06:35.994 --> 06:37.873
You help me a lot.
I'll treat you to a meal.

06:49.753 --> 06:50.833
Mr. Shen, here.

06:55.554 --> 06:56.073
You're home.

06:56.714 --> 06:57.193
Here.

06:58.154 --> 06:58.794
Thanks.

07:01.114 --> 07:02.073
I'll help you up.

07:03.193 --> 07:04.433
You don't need to come up.

07:04.594 --> 07:05.154
Are you okay?

07:05.674 --> 07:06.234
Sure.

07:07.234 --> 07:08.034
Be careful.

07:09.114 --> 07:09.873
I'm leaving.

07:11.313 --> 07:11.753
Okay.

08:02.554 --> 08:03.753
Shen Haoming's child

08:03.994 --> 08:05.753
had a paternity test in London.

08:07.273 --> 08:08.474
(Where is the test report?)

08:22.554 --> 08:23.474
Verification failed.

08:23.794 --> 08:25.273
Please try again.

08:27.234 --> 08:28.474
(Not his birthday.)

08:32.474 --> 08:34.194
Verification failed. Please try again.

08:34.234 --> 08:35.434
(Not his phone number.)

08:40.273 --> 08:40.913
Failed.

08:40.913 --> 08:41.793
(Not license plate.)

08:41.793 --> 08:42.873
Please try again.

08:43.194 --> 08:43.753
(Come on.)

08:44.673 --> 08:45.153
(I've)

08:45.153 --> 08:46.194
(failed three times.)

08:46.873 --> 08:48.393
(Another failure triggers the alarm.)

09:57.498 --> 10:00.368
(September 20, 2023)

10:25.354 --> 10:26.393
Verification passed.

10:38.810 --> 10:41.232
(Probability of paternity: 99.997%)

10:54.042 --> 10:56.460
(Jinda Group)

10:58.553 --> 10:59.553
Though it's pixelated,

10:59.834 --> 11:00.354
this building

11:00.354 --> 11:01.474
is our company, right?

11:03.706 --> 11:04.944
(Passing Off Illegitimate Son
as Younger Brother)

11:05.273 --> 11:06.834
He has a son out of wedlock?

11:06.994 --> 11:08.753
His family helped cover it up?

11:09.114 --> 11:09.594
Our company

11:09.594 --> 11:11.153
has such a scandalous executive?

11:12.762 --> 11:14.544
(Jinda Group Executive Shen Haoming
Passed Off Illegitimate Son as Brother)

11:14.994 --> 11:16.553
This happened so long ago.

11:17.273 --> 11:18.633
Why is it revealed now?

11:19.873 --> 11:21.354
Especially when Haoming

11:21.354 --> 11:22.834
just joined the board.

11:31.633 --> 11:32.114
Hello.

11:32.474 --> 11:33.114
Chairman,

11:33.153 --> 11:33.834
shareholders want

11:33.834 --> 11:34.913
an emergency board meeting.

11:34.994 --> 11:35.753
Come with Mr. Shen

11:35.753 --> 11:36.753
to the company now.

11:37.354 --> 11:37.954
Understood.

11:41.314 --> 11:41.793
Mom.

11:43.314 --> 11:44.074
I know.

11:58.753 --> 11:59.273
Liu,

11:59.633 --> 12:00.393
where is Haochen?

12:00.513 --> 12:01.673
Shen Haochen is in school.

12:01.753 --> 12:02.513
Ten minutes ago,

12:02.513 --> 12:03.314
he got there.

12:03.314 --> 12:05.114
Turn around and bring him home.

12:11.714 --> 12:12.194
Chen Lin.

12:12.873 --> 12:13.354
Find someone

12:13.834 --> 12:15.714
to remove all related news immediately.

12:15.994 --> 12:16.633
Inform the press

12:17.194 --> 12:18.673
this involves a minor

12:19.033 --> 12:20.354
and I can file a lawsuit anytime.

12:25.714 --> 12:26.314
Lin.

12:28.273 --> 12:28.834
Yan.

12:29.834 --> 12:30.753
Have you seen this?

12:31.114 --> 12:31.753
What?

12:44.633 --> 12:45.234
I'm going out.

12:45.234 --> 12:46.314
Cancel my schedule today.

12:46.393 --> 12:46.673
Okay.

12:46.793 --> 12:47.474
Be careful.

12:47.474 --> 12:48.176
(Jinda Group Executive Shen Haoming
Passed Off Illegitimate Son as Brother)

12:48.913 --> 12:50.273
My dad saw the news

12:50.393 --> 12:51.673
when he was driving me here.

12:53.234 --> 12:54.994
My dad even knows his brother.

12:55.474 --> 12:55.954
Wait.

12:56.234 --> 12:57.513
Now it's his dad.

12:57.793 --> 12:58.913
My mom saw it too.

12:59.074 --> 13:00.393
It's all over the internet now.

13:00.633 --> 13:01.354
Our class

13:01.434 --> 13:02.793
has a celebrity.

13:05.234 --> 13:06.393
What are you talking about?

13:06.793 --> 13:07.553
Shen Haochen,

13:07.633 --> 13:08.673
you've become

13:08.753 --> 13:09.714
a celebrity now.

13:11.434 --> 13:12.114
What do you mean?

13:12.393 --> 13:14.074
Don't tell me you didn't know

13:14.234 --> 13:15.393
your brother is your dad?

13:16.314 --> 13:17.354
Don't talk nonsense!

13:17.354 --> 13:18.673
Or I'll beat you to death!

13:18.834 --> 13:19.434
Stop it!

13:19.553 --> 13:20.114
Shen Haochen.

13:20.314 --> 13:21.074
Stop it!

13:25.673 --> 13:26.994
I got a call from your family.

13:27.673 --> 13:28.594
You have one day off.

13:29.074 --> 13:30.194
Go home with Mr. Liu.

13:31.153 --> 13:31.793
Thank you, Miss.

13:32.393 --> 13:33.434
Haochen, come with me.

13:34.714 --> 13:35.513
Thank you, Miss.

13:39.753 --> 13:40.434
Mr. Liu.

13:41.153 --> 13:42.314
Give me your phone.

13:45.786 --> 13:47.728
(Jinda Group Executive Shen Haoming
Passed Off Illegitimate Son as Brother)

13:50.434 --> 13:50.954
Mr. Qu.

13:52.273 --> 13:53.834
After exposure of Shen Haochen being

13:53.834 --> 13:55.114
Shen Haoming's illegitimate son,

13:55.594 --> 13:57.314
Jinda Group's stock price

13:57.314 --> 13:58.513
has dropped by 5.63 percent,

13:58.994 --> 14:00.553
losing at least
two billion market value.

14:02.194 --> 14:04.793
The Investment Department
suggests now is the time

14:04.793 --> 14:06.153
for a low-price acquisition.

14:07.834 --> 14:09.234
Tell them to start.

14:10.354 --> 14:10.834
Okay.

14:11.354 --> 14:13.194
Mr. Qu came

14:13.194 --> 14:14.633
from out of town today.

14:15.834 --> 14:16.354
Thank you.

14:16.834 --> 14:17.434
Alright.

14:17.753 --> 14:19.673
Today, everyone is present.

14:19.753 --> 14:20.873
Let's begin then.

14:31.594 --> 14:34.114
On behalf of everyone,

14:35.033 --> 14:36.194
I have a question.

14:36.834 --> 14:38.114
Online rumors say

14:38.553 --> 14:40.513
Haochen isn't your son,

14:40.954 --> 14:42.714
but Haoming's illegitimate son.

14:43.314 --> 14:46.033
Is that true

14:46.994 --> 14:48.033
or not?

14:49.834 --> 14:50.673
Regarding this,

14:50.834 --> 14:52.234
since its release online,

14:52.673 --> 14:54.314
in just three hours,

14:54.873 --> 14:56.033
our stock price has been

14:56.033 --> 14:56.954
continuously dropping.

14:57.194 --> 14:58.513
This has caused Jinda Group

14:58.873 --> 15:00.434
a huge loss.

15:02.074 --> 15:03.234
If it's fake,

15:04.033 --> 15:05.234
we must immediately

15:05.393 --> 15:06.234
issue a response.

15:06.434 --> 15:07.994
Make a statement where necessary,

15:08.234 --> 15:09.954
and prevent

15:10.194 --> 15:11.594
the further loss.

15:11.873 --> 15:13.194
How could this be fake?

15:13.594 --> 15:14.913
There is a paternity test report.

15:15.474 --> 15:16.393
In my opinion,

15:16.553 --> 15:18.114
it's most likely true.

15:18.513 --> 15:19.194
I wonder

15:19.234 --> 15:20.434
what the truth is.

15:21.354 --> 15:21.954
Chairman.

15:22.314 --> 15:23.273
At this critical moment,

15:23.594 --> 15:25.114
just tell us the truth.

15:25.474 --> 15:26.114
- Exactly.
- Exactly.

15:38.673 --> 15:39.553
Jinsong,

15:42.673 --> 15:45.954
all of us have followed you

15:47.194 --> 15:48.913
and suffered a lot

15:49.513 --> 15:50.474
to build Jinda

15:51.114 --> 15:52.434
from scratch.

15:52.834 --> 15:53.954
After the company grew,

15:54.793 --> 15:56.673
we all agreed

15:57.234 --> 15:59.234
to let you take leadership,

15:59.913 --> 16:01.753
because we believe

16:01.793 --> 16:02.553
you are trustworthy

16:03.434 --> 16:04.513
and could lead us all

16:04.673 --> 16:05.594
to make Jinda

16:05.793 --> 16:07.753
thrive smoothly.

16:08.474 --> 16:09.834
When this news broke out,

16:11.033 --> 16:12.994
we couldn't believe

16:12.994 --> 16:13.834
our own eyes.

16:14.673 --> 16:17.314
But the paternity test report

16:18.074 --> 16:19.314
is solid evidence,

16:20.913 --> 16:22.234
leaving no room for doubt.

16:23.673 --> 16:24.513
As a long-established

16:24.594 --> 16:25.994
construction group,

16:26.474 --> 16:29.074
if we lack basic ethical principles,

16:29.234 --> 16:30.434
how can we face the public?

16:30.954 --> 16:32.314
What reputation remains?

16:33.114 --> 16:34.513
What credibility remains?

16:34.954 --> 16:36.114
This damages our group's

16:36.114 --> 16:36.873
public image.

16:39.553 --> 16:40.153
Hear me out.

16:40.194 --> 16:41.633
My clients are pushing for answers.

16:43.873 --> 16:45.114
Are you my dad?

16:45.153 --> 16:45.873
We're in session.

16:46.114 --> 16:46.673
Leave for now.

16:46.714 --> 16:47.273
Answer me,

16:47.273 --> 16:48.474
are you my dad?

16:48.673 --> 16:49.594
We're in session.

16:49.673 --> 16:50.114
Get out!

16:50.114 --> 16:50.753
No!

16:50.753 --> 16:52.033
- Tell me now!
- Get out!

16:52.194 --> 16:52.793
No!

16:53.033 --> 16:53.994
- No!
- Get out!

16:54.074 --> 16:54.513
No!

16:54.513 --> 16:55.474
Are you my dad?

16:55.474 --> 16:56.114
Take him away.

16:56.354 --> 16:57.114
Answer me,

16:57.114 --> 16:58.434
are you my dad?

17:00.513 --> 17:01.474
Let me go!

17:02.994 --> 17:04.113
Let me go!

17:04.273 --> 17:05.474
Let me go!

17:05.753 --> 17:07.954
Answer my question!

17:08.474 --> 17:10.073
Are you my dad?

17:10.234 --> 17:11.954
Whose son am I really?

17:12.273 --> 17:13.434
Let me go!

17:15.313 --> 17:16.394
Answer me.

17:17.674 --> 17:19.434
Are you my dad?

17:19.753 --> 17:21.753
Who is my real dad?

17:22.793 --> 17:23.874
I just want to know

17:23.874 --> 17:25.073
if the online news

17:25.073 --> 17:26.714
is true.

17:29.434 --> 17:31.033
Are you my dad?

17:31.033 --> 17:32.234
Tell me!

17:32.353 --> 17:32.874
Haoming.

17:32.874 --> 17:33.154
Mom.

17:33.154 --> 17:34.434
I went to Haochen's school.

17:34.474 --> 17:36.234
His teacher said
the driver picked him up.

17:36.234 --> 17:37.593
He came to the office alone.

17:39.273 --> 17:40.553
Don't worry. He's safe.

17:40.553 --> 17:41.073
Okay.

17:41.434 --> 17:42.593
I'll arrange his ride home.

17:44.593 --> 17:46.194
If you're my dad,

17:46.793 --> 17:47.753
why tell me you're

17:47.753 --> 17:48.714
my brother?

17:49.553 --> 17:50.954
Where's my mom?

17:51.194 --> 17:52.513
Who is she really?

17:53.273 --> 17:55.273
Why did you lie?

17:56.113 --> 17:56.994
Do you never

17:56.994 --> 17:58.593
want me at all?

18:07.553 --> 18:08.394
I understand you have

18:08.434 --> 18:09.434
questions right now.

18:10.634 --> 18:11.434
Go home first.

18:13.194 --> 18:14.154
We'll talk later.

18:22.273 --> 18:22.833
Chen Lin,

18:23.914 --> 18:24.994
drive Haochen home.

18:25.474 --> 18:26.474
Yes, Mr. Shen.

18:26.954 --> 18:27.914
The board wants you

18:27.914 --> 18:29.394
to return to the meeting right away.

18:29.753 --> 18:30.313
Besides,

18:30.634 --> 18:31.434
many reporters

18:31.474 --> 18:32.194
are in the lobby.

18:32.474 --> 18:34.234
Bring my car to the underground garage.

18:34.833 --> 18:36.154
Don't let any reporter

18:36.154 --> 18:36.914
approach Haochen.

18:37.434 --> 18:37.914
Got it.

19:43.513 --> 19:44.553
Don't overthink.

19:45.553 --> 19:47.073
Ignore the online news.

19:48.634 --> 19:49.394
Wait for me.

20:17.593 --> 20:19.033
The Chairman's family matters

20:19.994 --> 20:21.753
shouldn't concern us,

20:22.073 --> 20:23.234
but you father and son

20:23.914 --> 20:25.793
are our core leadership.

20:26.874 --> 20:28.194
Your every action

20:29.273 --> 20:31.434
reflects the image,

20:31.434 --> 20:35.353
reputation, and integrity of the group.

20:37.154 --> 20:37.954
Jinsong,

20:39.033 --> 20:40.073
any solutions?

20:40.793 --> 20:41.634
Just tell us

20:42.914 --> 20:45.113
and be honest to us.

20:45.753 --> 20:47.033
Let us know clearly.

20:48.273 --> 20:49.674
Don't drag this on.

20:50.113 --> 20:50.474
Exactly.

20:50.634 --> 20:51.634
We must

20:51.674 --> 20:53.874
address this problem.

20:54.033 --> 20:57.353
You've caused us pressure
while tricking customers.

20:57.674 --> 20:58.194
Exactly.

20:58.553 --> 20:59.313
Your silence

20:59.394 --> 21:01.234
leaves us unable to explain anything.

21:01.714 --> 21:03.194
You must explain to us.

21:04.593 --> 21:05.073
Haoming.

21:08.073 --> 21:08.793
Haoming.

21:16.874 --> 21:18.553
Dad, are you feeling unwell?

21:21.234 --> 21:22.194
The Chairman isn't well.

21:22.313 --> 21:23.273
Let's end it for now.

21:28.113 --> 21:29.154
Listen to me.

21:30.714 --> 21:32.073
The Chairman isn't feeling well.

21:32.234 --> 21:33.353
No matter what,

21:33.793 --> 21:35.033
we shouldn't pressure him.

21:35.833 --> 21:36.994
Anyway,

21:37.994 --> 21:39.353
this situation can't get worse.

21:39.753 --> 21:40.833
Let's wait and see.

21:41.674 --> 21:42.994
Let's see how long

21:44.113 --> 21:45.353
he can stall.

21:53.113 --> 21:54.874
Dad. Take the medicine.

21:57.954 --> 21:58.513
Put it there.

22:13.553 --> 22:14.674
Chairman, Mr. Shen.

22:16.954 --> 22:17.553
What's wrong?

22:17.954 --> 22:18.753
Several companies

22:18.753 --> 22:19.553
are acquiring

22:19.553 --> 22:20.553
large quantities

22:20.553 --> 22:21.313
of Jinda's stocks.

22:21.954 --> 22:23.793
The main buyer is Situo Construction.

22:25.113 --> 22:25.833
It is the one

22:25.994 --> 22:26.914
that competed with us

22:26.914 --> 22:28.434
for the Baraikin project.

22:29.073 --> 22:29.874
How many stocks?

22:30.273 --> 22:31.194
3.7 percent of stocks,

22:31.234 --> 22:32.234
and it's increasing.

22:38.714 --> 22:39.313
Haoming.

22:40.513 --> 22:42.714
Initiate buybacks immediately.

22:43.033 --> 22:44.273
This shows market

22:44.273 --> 22:45.793
our confidence.

23:10.994 --> 23:11.833
Shen Haochen!

23:13.674 --> 23:14.434
Haochen!

23:19.450 --> 23:20.752
(Secretary Chen)

23:21.313 --> 23:21.714
Hello.

23:21.874 --> 23:22.593
Mr. Shen,

23:22.994 --> 23:24.474
Haochen opened the car door

23:24.634 --> 23:25.954
during a red light and ran off.

23:26.714 --> 23:27.833
He disappeared

23:28.513 --> 23:29.674
before I could catch up.

23:50.113 --> 23:50.674
Haochen.

23:51.674 --> 23:52.553
Why are you here?

23:53.593 --> 23:54.353
Mr. Han.

23:55.674 --> 23:56.954
I know what happened today.

23:58.394 --> 23:59.313
You must feel

23:59.313 --> 24:00.313
terrible now.

24:01.553 --> 24:02.793
Come on, I'll take you home.

24:04.154 --> 24:04.833
No.

24:05.954 --> 24:07.553
Do you want to know who your mom is?

24:10.674 --> 24:11.194
Yes!

24:11.593 --> 24:12.714
I'll take you to see her.

24:34.234 --> 24:34.674
We're here.

24:40.073 --> 24:40.874
Didn't you say

24:40.874 --> 24:41.994
to see my mom?

24:42.113 --> 24:43.273
Why bring me here?

24:43.674 --> 24:45.033
To protect your mom's identity

24:45.033 --> 24:46.033
from revealing.

24:48.553 --> 24:49.273
I got it.

24:49.874 --> 24:50.434
Now,

24:51.113 --> 24:51.793
I'll take you in

24:51.793 --> 24:52.674
and get some rest.

24:52.914 --> 24:53.674
Wait for me there.

24:53.994 --> 24:54.674
Don't run around.

24:55.033 --> 24:55.914
I'll fetch your mom.

24:56.994 --> 24:57.513
Okay?

24:58.394 --> 24:58.793
Okay.

25:04.634 --> 25:05.634
What did the police say?

25:06.753 --> 25:08.434
They've filed a report.

25:08.793 --> 25:11.593
They are checking surveillance footage,
and dispatching officers

25:11.593 --> 25:12.714
to Haochen's usual spots

25:12.833 --> 25:13.634
to search for him.

25:14.874 --> 25:16.753
Yan has already gone

25:16.874 --> 25:18.194
to check Haochen's usual spots.

25:18.353 --> 25:19.874
If Yan finds him, she will tell me.

25:20.553 --> 25:21.194
Haoming.

25:21.194 --> 25:21.753
Don't worry.

25:23.553 --> 25:24.194
How is Dad?

25:25.073 --> 25:27.033
I didn't tell him
about Haochen's situation.

25:28.073 --> 25:29.874
I let him rest upstairs for a while.

25:30.273 --> 25:31.194
I'll tell him

25:31.194 --> 25:32.154
when possible.

25:32.474 --> 25:32.914
Okay.

25:34.434 --> 25:34.954
Mom.

25:35.553 --> 25:36.914
Haochen will definitely be fine.

25:37.313 --> 25:38.194
Don't worry.

25:39.194 --> 25:39.874
Many reporters

25:39.874 --> 25:40.753
are out there.

25:41.434 --> 25:44.313
You should stay here

25:44.434 --> 25:45.313
for now.

25:46.154 --> 25:46.553
Alright.

25:47.033 --> 25:47.994
I need to go out

25:48.313 --> 25:49.194
to look for Haochen.

25:49.714 --> 25:50.394
Haoming.

26:04.353 --> 26:05.434
Haochen's backpack!

26:08.634 --> 26:11.632
(Yongxiang)

26:13.113 --> 26:14.313
Yongxiang Building?

26:23.033 --> 26:23.793
Officer Liu.

26:24.434 --> 26:25.874
I just received a photo.

26:26.394 --> 26:27.513
It's Haochen's backpack.

26:28.154 --> 26:29.874
Location is Yongxiang Building.

26:30.273 --> 26:30.874
Please

26:31.273 --> 26:32.353
dispatch officers.

26:33.113 --> 26:33.753
Thank you.

26:38.273 --> 26:38.833
Yan.

26:39.313 --> 26:39.954
Where are you?

27:13.833 --> 27:14.674
Han Weiping?

27:20.434 --> 27:21.313
Wait for the police.

27:46.194 --> 27:46.914
Where is Haochen?

27:48.793 --> 27:49.474
Mr. Shen.

27:50.313 --> 27:51.394
What are you doing?

27:52.634 --> 27:53.994
I didn't harm Haochen.

27:54.194 --> 27:55.714
You are the ones who harmed him.

27:56.154 --> 27:56.914
He wants to know

27:56.954 --> 27:57.874
who his mom is.

27:57.954 --> 27:58.793
Is he wrong?

27:59.194 --> 28:00.994
You're the ones who kept lying to him.

28:00.994 --> 28:01.793
Not me.

28:02.033 --> 28:03.273
Where is Haochen?

28:04.914 --> 28:07.234
The innermost room on the second floor.

28:22.113 --> 28:22.674
Haochen!

28:24.914 --> 28:25.434
Haoming!

28:31.273 --> 28:31.914
Are you okay?

28:38.154 --> 28:38.914
Thank you.

28:38.914 --> 28:40.353
It's okay. We're just doing our job.

28:40.513 --> 28:41.154
He is fine.

28:41.833 --> 28:42.914
Please help us

28:42.994 --> 28:44.313
with a statement later.

28:45.073 --> 28:45.634
No problem.

28:45.634 --> 28:46.394
Thank you.

28:48.793 --> 28:49.234
Be careful.

28:49.753 --> 28:50.273
I'm fine.

28:55.394 --> 28:57.313
They're coming out!

28:58.073 --> 28:59.593
We're on official duty.

28:59.593 --> 29:00.113
Step back!

29:03.593 --> 29:04.033
Haoming.

29:05.434 --> 29:07.234
It's okay. Stay behind me.

29:07.714 --> 29:08.874
- Mr. Shen!
- Mr. Shen!

29:08.994 --> 29:10.033
Make way, please!

29:10.033 --> 29:10.793
Shen Haochen...

29:10.833 --> 29:11.753
No interviews.

29:12.593 --> 29:13.033
Mr. Shen.

29:13.073 --> 29:13.674
Is Shen Haochen

29:13.674 --> 29:14.474
really your son?

29:14.553 --> 29:15.313
If it's not true,

29:15.313 --> 29:17.033
how do you explain the paternity test?

29:17.313 --> 29:18.234
If it is true,

29:18.313 --> 29:19.273
why didn't you

29:19.313 --> 29:20.474
acknowledge him as your son?

29:20.793 --> 29:21.833
Do you never want...

29:21.874 --> 29:22.914
Haochen. Look at me!

29:23.793 --> 29:24.353
Let me go!

29:24.553 --> 29:25.394
Don't hold me!

29:25.434 --> 29:26.394
Let me go!

29:26.753 --> 29:28.154
Let me go!

29:33.313 --> 29:34.194
It is okay now.

29:38.994 --> 29:40.874
It seems Shen Haochen
also wants the truth.

29:40.954 --> 29:42.513
Can you tell us the truth?

29:53.874 --> 29:54.793
You're my son.

29:56.234 --> 29:56.714
Mr. Shen.

29:56.714 --> 29:58.634
You just admitted
he is your son out of wedlock.

29:58.954 --> 30:00.194
Who is his real mom?

30:00.273 --> 30:00.833
Where is she?

30:01.474 --> 30:03.273
Rumors say you are getting divorced.

30:03.793 --> 30:05.234
Is Shen Haochen the reason for it?

30:05.434 --> 30:06.994
How's your marriage now?

30:07.353 --> 30:09.194
It's said
Haochen's biological mom drowned.

30:09.313 --> 30:10.714
Did you know about this earlier?

30:10.753 --> 30:11.634
How will you face

30:11.634 --> 30:12.154
the child?

30:12.154 --> 30:13.753
This child is my son.

30:17.234 --> 30:18.994
I am Shen Haochen's mom.

30:20.714 --> 30:21.634
You've all seen it.

30:21.753 --> 30:22.553
My son is not

30:22.553 --> 30:23.353
feeling well.

30:24.154 --> 30:24.753
I hope that you

30:24.753 --> 30:25.994
have professional integrity.

30:26.073 --> 30:27.073
Don't harass

30:27.113 --> 30:27.954
a minor.

30:28.634 --> 30:29.753
We are doing fine.

30:30.273 --> 30:31.033
Don't worry.

30:31.434 --> 30:32.914
But if you continue doing so,

30:33.154 --> 30:34.353
we'll file a lawsuit.

30:34.553 --> 30:35.234
Please make way.

30:36.394 --> 30:37.273
Make way!

31:01.313 --> 31:01.954
Haochen.

31:06.033 --> 31:06.833
You haven't eaten

31:06.833 --> 31:07.954
all day.

31:11.793 --> 31:13.634
Here's your favorite spareribs,

31:14.634 --> 31:15.674
rice balls,

31:15.793 --> 31:17.194
and pumpkin cubes.

31:17.793 --> 31:19.194
All your favorite food.

31:19.593 --> 31:20.273
It smells good.

31:20.353 --> 31:21.434
Let's eat a little,

31:21.474 --> 31:21.994
okay?

31:22.753 --> 31:23.353
Smell it.

31:29.553 --> 31:31.073
Who's that thoughtful,

31:31.394 --> 31:32.353
preparing Haochen's

31:32.353 --> 31:33.434
favorite cola?

31:33.833 --> 31:34.674
It's still cold.

31:35.273 --> 31:35.793
Haochen.

31:38.954 --> 31:40.394
Please eat

31:40.434 --> 31:41.634
or drink something.

31:43.073 --> 31:43.553
We're really

31:43.553 --> 31:45.073
worried about you!

31:45.954 --> 31:47.273
Haochen, please.

31:49.714 --> 31:50.634
Haochen, come on.

31:50.634 --> 31:52.273
Don't scare me.

31:52.313 --> 31:53.234
Say something.

31:54.073 --> 31:55.113
Let's go out.

31:55.753 --> 31:57.154
Do anything you want.

31:59.353 --> 32:00.954
Please say something, Haochen.

32:00.994 --> 32:01.674
Please.

32:01.674 --> 32:03.434
We're all worried about you!

32:03.474 --> 32:04.194
Haochen.

32:11.113 --> 32:13.874
Shareholders demand another meeting.
Dad is already there.

32:14.154 --> 32:14.833
I must go.

32:14.954 --> 32:15.674
You got this.

32:15.994 --> 32:17.394
Don't worry. I got this.

32:17.833 --> 32:18.833
You and Dad take care.

32:28.793 --> 32:33.154
You're here? I get flowers for you.

32:43.593 --> 32:44.154
What's wrong?

32:50.593 --> 32:54.313
Did you disclose
the paternity test report?

32:56.553 --> 32:57.674
What paternity test report?

32:58.313 --> 32:59.033
I don't know.

33:00.634 --> 33:01.313
Han Weiping.

33:01.914 --> 33:02.833
Stop pretending!

33:03.353 --> 33:04.073
Only you

33:04.474 --> 33:05.273
kept asking about

33:05.273 --> 33:06.593
my sister and Shen Haoming.

33:07.714 --> 33:08.994
Yes, it was me.

33:12.513 --> 33:13.353
Please leave.

33:15.073 --> 33:17.154
Between us, there will be
no more contact.

33:27.898 --> 33:31.344
(Parallel to Big Dipper)

33:34.833 --> 33:36.194
Shen Jinsong.

33:36.240 --> 33:38.874
(2019 Most Influential Entrepreneurs
No. 32: Shen Jinsong)

33:38.874 --> 33:39.954
Entrepreneur.

33:44.833 --> 33:45.753
Qu,

33:47.593 --> 33:50.914
you have 12 percent of shares

33:50.954 --> 33:54.994
of Jinda Group.

33:55.634 --> 33:56.313
Right?

33:57.353 --> 34:00.313
Now I have 16.3 percent.

34:01.553 --> 34:02.994
You initiated buybacks

34:04.234 --> 34:06.593
and capped the shares

34:06.634 --> 34:07.833
Situo bought

34:07.914 --> 34:09.354
below 5 percent.

34:10.994 --> 34:12.033
I won by a narrow margin.

34:13.274 --> 34:14.474
Situo

34:14.954 --> 34:17.193
predicted Jinda's trouble.

34:21.633 --> 34:22.274
Haoming,

34:24.633 --> 34:26.914
there's a mole in Jinda.

34:27.914 --> 34:28.593
Otherwise,

34:29.474 --> 34:30.553
Situo wouldn't have

34:30.954 --> 34:32.394
reserved massive funds

34:32.394 --> 34:33.713
to buy shares.

34:34.394 --> 34:35.994
And this mole

34:36.994 --> 34:39.314
is the one who leaked

34:41.314 --> 34:42.274
Haochen's identity.

34:44.874 --> 34:46.274
I just never imagined

34:46.593 --> 34:48.113
it was you.

34:49.073 --> 34:50.474
You should've expected this.

34:51.474 --> 34:53.553
I have been excluded
by you for so many years.

34:55.233 --> 34:56.073
I have attended

34:57.113 --> 34:58.874
few board meetings, right?

34:59.193 --> 35:00.474
Just once or twice.

35:00.994 --> 35:02.834
I was just speaking

35:03.033 --> 35:03.994
on conference calls.

35:05.713 --> 35:06.794
Did you forget

35:06.794 --> 35:07.713
about me?

35:09.354 --> 35:11.673
Holding onto such resentment,

35:16.474 --> 35:17.874
you've had a hard time pretending.

35:20.274 --> 35:21.314
For decades,

35:21.314 --> 35:23.033
you've been acting

35:23.033 --> 35:24.394
like my best buddy

35:24.394 --> 35:26.274
in front of everyone.

35:31.434 --> 35:32.394
We started

35:33.394 --> 35:34.834
the business from scratch together.

35:35.754 --> 35:36.874
But after we expanded,

35:38.434 --> 35:39.754
you became a dictator.

35:40.713 --> 35:42.153
We had to obey your orders.

35:43.994 --> 35:45.874
All our founding buddies

35:45.874 --> 35:46.673
from the early days

35:47.633 --> 35:49.274
got exiled by you

35:49.274 --> 35:50.513
far from Jingzhou.

35:51.354 --> 35:52.073
Every one of them.

35:52.233 --> 35:52.874
Think about it.

35:55.394 --> 35:56.073
Like me,

35:57.994 --> 36:00.914
I have worked in Guangdong for 30 years.

36:01.954 --> 36:03.153
If I hadn't explored

36:03.794 --> 36:05.153
the market of Hong Kong, China

36:06.113 --> 36:07.994
and defended my territory,

36:09.513 --> 36:13.794
you would kick me out anytime.

36:17.153 --> 36:17.673
Enough.

36:18.394 --> 36:19.314
You've occupied

36:19.994 --> 36:21.193
this position for decades.

36:22.633 --> 36:23.914
Time for someone new.

36:30.073 --> 36:31.474
Your beard has turned white,

36:33.113 --> 36:34.954
and you aimed at a child?

36:36.434 --> 36:37.673
How despicable!

36:40.233 --> 36:41.754
There's an old saying,

36:42.073 --> 36:46.233
"always hit where it hurts."

36:46.874 --> 36:48.314
It's a fight,

36:49.434 --> 36:50.834
so why care about morals?

36:55.354 --> 36:56.033
Haoming.

36:57.834 --> 36:59.033
Han Weiping

36:59.914 --> 37:01.073
is your lawyer, right?

37:03.794 --> 37:05.153
He's my godson.

37:23.233 --> 37:24.434
That bad guy!

37:28.713 --> 37:29.113
Dad!

37:30.153 --> 37:31.073
Dad! Dad!

37:33.553 --> 37:34.274
Help!

37:35.713 --> 37:36.794
Call an ambulance!

37:39.066 --> 37:42.608
(Jingzhou Yuekang Hospital)

37:50.153 --> 37:50.633
Doctor,

37:51.593 --> 37:52.113
how is he?

37:52.434 --> 37:53.153
The surgery

37:53.394 --> 37:54.434
was successful.

37:55.073 --> 37:56.713
The patient had a ruptured aneurysm

37:56.994 --> 37:58.474
with subarachnoid hemorrhage.

37:58.874 --> 37:59.553
The surgery

37:59.593 --> 38:00.193
has stabilized

38:00.193 --> 38:01.233
his condition.

38:03.394 --> 38:04.593
When will he wake up?

38:05.153 --> 38:06.794
It is hard to tell.

38:06.994 --> 38:07.914
So you should

38:08.233 --> 38:09.754
be prepared.

38:23.193 --> 38:23.593
Mom,

38:24.914 --> 38:25.633
it's okay.

38:27.834 --> 38:29.434
Let's wait patiently until Dad wakes up.

38:29.513 --> 38:29.874
Okay?

38:30.193 --> 38:30.994
Don't worry.

38:32.193 --> 38:33.233
Your dad

38:34.954 --> 38:36.314
has managed the group for years.

38:40.513 --> 38:41.593
We've weathered

38:41.593 --> 38:42.754
countless storms together.

38:46.033 --> 38:46.713
He'll overcome

38:49.754 --> 38:50.874
this hurdle too.

38:52.033 --> 38:53.073
He definitely will.

38:56.073 --> 38:57.354
You look exhausted.

38:58.153 --> 38:59.673
I'll stay here.

38:59.874 --> 39:01.073
Go home and rest. Okay?

39:01.794 --> 39:02.314
No need.

39:13.274 --> 39:14.874
I'm staying here.

39:16.713 --> 39:18.513
I need to see him wake up.

39:24.713 --> 39:26.914
Qu Mingcheng schemed against your dad.

39:28.314 --> 39:30.193
I won't let him get away with this.

39:36.474 --> 39:36.914
Hello.

39:37.474 --> 39:37.954
Haoming,

39:38.394 --> 39:39.593
how's your dad now?

39:40.954 --> 39:41.914
He is out of surgery.

39:42.673 --> 39:43.914
It is still uncertain.

39:46.274 --> 39:46.914
I'll stay

39:46.954 --> 39:48.113
with Mom at the hospital.

39:48.954 --> 39:49.994
Help take care of Haochen.

39:51.633 --> 39:52.193
I see.

39:52.874 --> 39:54.073
I'll stay with Haochen.

39:54.673 --> 39:55.474
Don't worry.

39:56.113 --> 39:57.233
Dad will definitely recover.

40:11.354 --> 40:12.113
Has he eaten?

40:12.754 --> 40:13.593
No.

40:14.354 --> 40:15.754
He stays locked in his room,

40:15.754 --> 40:17.193
without saying a word.

40:17.834 --> 40:18.834
He's usually

40:19.233 --> 40:20.233
such an energetic child.

40:20.233 --> 40:20.834
But now...

40:24.794 --> 40:25.713
I'll go, Hui.

40:36.274 --> 40:36.954
Haochen.

40:37.874 --> 40:38.874
I'm coming in.

41:00.593 --> 41:01.193
Haochen.

41:02.153 --> 41:03.994
If you don't eat,

41:04.954 --> 41:06.274
your body will collapse.

41:17.274 --> 41:18.474
How about this?

41:28.633 --> 41:29.153
Look.

41:29.874 --> 41:31.113
I'll leave

41:31.113 --> 41:32.233
a pen and notebook here.

41:32.874 --> 41:33.914
We'll talk through this.

41:34.553 --> 41:35.474
Write down whatever

41:35.474 --> 41:36.274
you want to eat.

41:38.314 --> 41:38.794
Okay?

41:53.474 --> 41:55.193
It's a beautiful day today.

41:55.954 --> 41:57.113
And the sun isn't too strong.

41:58.153 --> 42:01.193
Perfect for skateboarding.

42:01.434 --> 42:02.233
Want to go out?

42:07.233 --> 42:08.233
You don't want to go out

42:12.633 --> 42:18.434
or speak? You don't want to talk to me?

42:24.553 --> 42:25.153
Alright then.

42:27.394 --> 42:28.553
I'll stay here with you.

42:28.593 --> 42:29.073
Okay?

42:30.794 --> 42:31.713
Good boy, Haochen.

43:32.354 --> 43:33.033
Jinsong.

43:36.193 --> 43:37.754
Haoming and I are both here with you.

43:40.394 --> 43:41.673
You must wake up.

43:45.834 --> 43:47.153
We're waiting for you.

43:56.474 --> 43:58.033
You must wake up.

44:15.314 --> 44:15.914
Haoming,

44:19.033 --> 44:19.994
I check on your dad.

44:20.673 --> 44:21.153
Here.

44:22.513 --> 44:23.633
Mom, let me introduce.

44:23.754 --> 44:24.914
Yu Yiming, Dr. Yu,

44:25.553 --> 44:27.434
the boyfriend of Xu Yan's sister.

44:28.434 --> 44:28.914
Hello.

44:29.033 --> 44:29.553
Hello.

44:35.033 --> 44:35.914
How is he doing?

44:37.073 --> 44:40.754
He is conscious, with stable condition.

44:41.513 --> 44:42.914
But he's not awake.

44:44.274 --> 44:45.314
It is good enough.

44:46.593 --> 44:47.513
It takes time.

44:47.914 --> 44:49.113
He has just had surgery

44:49.314 --> 44:50.394
and needs time to recover.

44:53.354 --> 44:53.834
Madam.

44:54.834 --> 44:56.113
His attending physician

44:56.314 --> 44:57.354
is my mentor's classmate,

44:58.153 --> 44:59.713
also the expert in neurosurgery.

44:59.954 --> 45:00.914
I just met him

45:01.394 --> 45:01.994
and asked him

45:02.474 --> 45:03.434
to pay more attention.

45:04.834 --> 45:05.954
Thank you, Yu.

45:06.874 --> 45:07.394
No problem.

45:07.633 --> 45:08.233
It's nothing.

45:08.314 --> 45:09.113
We're family.

45:09.713 --> 45:11.434
Thank you for coming.

45:13.713 --> 45:14.673
He needs rest.

45:16.033 --> 45:17.033
I'll take my leave.

45:17.553 --> 45:18.673
I just want to say

45:19.354 --> 45:20.314
if you need any help,

45:20.394 --> 45:21.153
tell me anytime.

45:21.513 --> 45:23.513
I can help you
with night shifts and rotations.

45:24.794 --> 45:25.314
Thank you.

45:26.434 --> 45:27.153
Rest assured.

45:27.673 --> 45:28.153
Thank you.

45:28.513 --> 45:29.233
I'm going back.

45:38.233 --> 45:38.954
Where's the child?

45:40.474 --> 45:41.113
In his room.

45:43.354 --> 45:46.073
He doesn't eat, drink, or say a word.

45:47.874 --> 45:48.994
I don't know what to do.

45:49.073 --> 45:52.073
But I can just stay with him.

45:55.994 --> 45:58.394
While caring for him,
you also take care of yourself.

45:59.314 --> 46:00.834
Yu Yiming went to the hospital.

46:02.033 --> 46:02.513
Okay.

46:04.553 --> 46:05.673
Thank you and Yiming.

46:09.153 --> 46:11.593
I've been swamped lately.

46:11.713 --> 46:12.954
So please take care

46:13.673 --> 46:14.513
of the company.

46:15.073 --> 46:16.394
Rest assured.

46:18.233 --> 46:19.434
With such a big incident,

46:19.633 --> 46:21.193
Haoming must be concerned too.

46:21.593 --> 46:23.033
His father and son need his care.

46:25.073 --> 46:25.474
It's okay.

46:25.914 --> 46:26.513
You stay here

46:26.513 --> 46:27.434
and share his burdens.

46:27.633 --> 46:28.834
We've got the company covered.

46:33.033 --> 46:34.593
Gubei Town's botanical dyeing project

46:34.673 --> 46:36.153
and our physical stores

46:36.274 --> 46:37.354
are progressing as usual.

46:37.994 --> 46:39.113
If you have any question,

46:39.153 --> 46:40.354
just call me.

46:40.513 --> 46:42.073
Got it. Don't worry.

46:46.914 --> 46:47.474
Have water.

46:59.553 --> 47:00.153
Hello. Lin.

47:00.994 --> 47:01.553
Yiming.

47:02.193 --> 47:03.673
I just met Yan.

47:03.874 --> 47:04.274
I have

47:04.274 --> 47:05.153
met the doctor

47:05.593 --> 47:06.394
and told Haoming

47:06.434 --> 47:08.754
to call us anytime

47:08.834 --> 47:09.593
if he needs help.

47:10.834 --> 47:11.553
I've told her too.

47:12.834 --> 47:13.474
Yiming.

47:13.673 --> 47:15.394
Yan has been swamped lately.

47:15.914 --> 47:17.274
I need to take care

47:17.274 --> 47:18.354
of Yan Studio.

47:18.874 --> 47:21.233
Wait until this busy period ends,

47:21.233 --> 47:22.754
I'll make it up to you.

47:24.193 --> 47:25.113
Special times.

47:25.314 --> 47:25.954
I understand.

47:26.673 --> 47:27.794
Let's help share

47:27.914 --> 47:28.673
their burdens.

47:29.513 --> 47:30.233
But don't

47:30.233 --> 47:31.113
overwork yourself.

47:31.754 --> 47:32.394
Love you!

47:33.033 --> 47:33.874
I'll hang up.

47:34.874 --> 47:35.354
Okay.

47:35.834 --> 47:36.314
Bye.

47:55.033 --> 47:55.553
Thank you.

47:56.394 --> 47:56.954
You're here.

